description._content: Repository: California Historical Society Digital object ID: Kemble Spec Col 09_B220 Call Number: Kemble Spec Col 09 Collection: California Lettersheet Collection Date: Undated Physical Description: Wood engraving; 10 x 19 cm. General Note: Barber & Baker. Scope and Contents: Shows Sackett's Hotel in Sacramento, with signs for Barr Griggs & Coursen, State Treasurer, Merchants Exchange, W.M. Hares & Co., and other storefronts. Preferred citation: [Sackett's Hotel.], California Lettersheet Collection, Kemble Spec Col 09, courtesy, California Historical Society, Kemble Spec Col 09_B220.
